subject: problem with getTableWithID
msgSnippet: The test was built with unit test release 1.4 we upgraded to 1.6 and not the test appears to not work 100%.  By this I use it on several pages without problem
messageBody:
The test was built with unit test release 1.4 we upgraded to 1.6 and
not the test appears to not work 100%. By this I use it on several
pages without problem except on the first screen. I can not get it to
find the table with the specific id. I have even gone back through
the prior releases to see when my issue would have surfaced. I found
that the problem is with 1.4.6 and forward. I have run the html
through several html validators and they don't have any major issues,
just missing 4.01 attributes that are not required.

I'm at a loss for what to do next, any ideas on what to look for or
could someone provide another pair of eyes to look at the code?

Any help is greatly appreciated.
Thanks Jeff
